sections.heading: 19. Frames and iFrames-- Not Applicable to Documents
content: -   Frames and iframes are not implemented in non-web documents, so this test is not applicable. It was not removed to maintain harmonization with the ICT Testing Baseline for Web.

sections.heading: Test Results
content: -   Baseline Tests 19.A-FrameTitle and 19.B-iFrameName are not applicable to documents
